Honoring Hotel Lakeside on its One Hundred Fiftieth
Anniversary.
WHEREAS, The members of the Senate of the 136th General Assembly 1
of Ohio are pleased to commend Hotel Lakeside on the occasion of its 2
One Hundred Fiftieth Anniversary and rededication ceremony, celebrated 3
August 2, 2025; and 4
WHEREAS, A notable local landmark listed on the National Register 5
of Historic Places, Hotel Lakeside holds a unique place in the history 6
of the area, and it is fitting that the anniversary of this building 7
be enthusiastically commemorated. Built in 1875, the hotel has 8
welcomed numerous dignitaries and celebrities and witnessed many 9
changes over the decades, including expansions, renovations, and the 10
addition of running water, plumbing, and electricity, but poor 11
maintenance and neglect brought it to the brink of dereliction. 12
Fortunately, the building was saved from destruction and carefully 13
restored over the course of more than four decades, and it now stands 14
as an example of the rich heritage of bygone days; and 15
