in, its exciting and colorful past, and the memorializing of 17
significant landmarks and artifacts is vital to the preservation of 18
Americaâ€™s unique heritage. Indeed, the continued longevity of Hotel 19
Lakeside is a justifiable source of pride and an outstanding 20
reflection on the many people who have supported its refurbishing, 21
including its board of trustees and the Friends of Hotel Lakeside, and 22
on the entire community; and 23
WHEREAS, The conservation of the Hotel Lakeside building can be 24
attributed to the vision and foresight of a host of innovative 25
individuals, and all those who have been involved with the 26

